name: VR Horror Stories
summary: VR Horror Stories" leverages virtual reality to place viewers directly in the middle of the action,  enhancing the fear and suspense for a more intense experience.  The collection comprises 17 short 360° horror videos, totaling 46 minutes in duration, each enhanced with immersive and spine-chilling sound effects. Explore dialogue-free scary experiences and English narrative stories with multilingual subtitles support through a user-friendly interface for seamless navigation and enjoyment.
